text: Netta is a genus of diving ducks. Netta may also refer to: ==People== *Netta Barzilai (born 1993), Israeli singer also known mononymously as Netta *Johnetta "Netta" Elzie, American civil rights activist * Netta Garti (born 1980), Israeli actress ==Places== *Netta (river) in north-east Poland *Netta (village), near Augustów in north-east Poland, comprising: **Netta Pierwsza (Netta I) **Netta Druga (Netta II) **Netta-Folwark ==Other== *Netta, an introductory form of netball ==See also== *
